*libglademm-2.4.1 (11 Dec 2004)

  11 Dec 2004; Joe McCann <joem@gentoo.org> +libglademm-2.4.1.ebuild:
  version bump which fixed gcc-3.4 compile. No need to patch any more.

  07 Nov 2004; Karol Wojtaszek <sekretarz@gentoo.org>
  +files/libglademm-2.2.0-configure.patch, libglademm-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Fixed linking problems on amd64, bug #57987

  05 Oct 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> libglademm-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

  06 Sep 2004; Karol Wojtaszek <sekretarz@gentoo.org> libglademm-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Fixed gcc-3.4 issues. Thanks to Chris Arepantis <ChrisArepantis@gmail.com> in
  bug #57318

